---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case ID           |     UC001                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     
|---------------------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case   Name       |     Register Yourself                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Created By            |     Mr.ABC        |       Last Updated By     4th May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                          
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Date Created          |     1 May 2019    |       Last Revision By    1st May 2020                                                                                                                                                                                                            
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Actors                |     Customer                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Pre   Conditions      |     Internet   Connectivity, Browser Compatibility                                                                                                                                                                                                                            
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Post Conditions       |     A new user   is created                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Basic Flow            |     Customer goes to the registration page.
|                           |     Customer fills   all the details like ID and password     
|                           |     If all the   data is valid , then he will be registered.     
|                           |     Confirmation   mail is send to the new user.                                                        
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Alternate   Flow      |     If the   entered username is already present in the system, then an error message will pop up saying that the user already exists.           
|                           |     If any   compulsory field is left blank then a error message will pop up saying all   compulsory fields must be filled.    
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Exceptional   Flow    |     If the Customer   encounters any technical errors while filling the registration form.                                                                                                                                                                                    
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Assumptions           |     Customer have   basic knowledge of computer and English                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Constraints           |     username   cannot be name(It should be email id)                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Dependencies          |     None                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Input &   Output      |     Input->   Username and Password     Output->   Password                                                                                                                                                                                                                   
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Business   Rule       |     Username->   valid, unique email id     
|                           |      Password->   1 capital letter, 1 small letter, 1 number, 1 special character, Last 5 passwords cannot be repeated, password should have 8 to 10 characters.                                                                 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

