|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
|     Use Case Name       |     Login                                                                                                                                                                                                                          
|     Created By          |     Mr.ABC               Last   Updated By                4th   May 2020                                                                                                                                                          
|     Date Created        |     1 May 2019       Last   Revision By                 1st   May 2020                                                                                                                                                             
|     Actors              |     Customer, Admin, Delivery Boy                                                                                                                                                                                                  
|     Pre Conditions      |     Internet Connectivity, Browser Compatibility                                                                                                                                                                                   
|     Post Conditions     |     Home page for actor should be displayed                                                                                                                                                                                        
|     Basic Flow          |     Username and Password are correct                                                                                                                                                                                             
|     Alternate Flow      |     Password is wrong, Username is wrong, Both are wrong                                                                                                                                                                           
|     Exceptional Flow    |     Forgot password, Forgot username                                                                                                                                                                                              
|     Assumptions         |     User have basic knowledge of computer and English                                                                                                                                                                              
|     Constraints         |     username cannot be name(It should be email id)                                                                                                                                                                                 
|     Dependencies        |     User should exist-> a Registration Process should be there                                                                                                                                                                    
|     Input & Output      |     Input-> Username and Password     Output-> Status flag or error code                                                                                                                                                           
|     Business Rule       |     Username-> valid, unique email id     Password-> 1 capital letter, 1 small letter, 1 number, 1   special character,     Last 5 passwords cannot be repeated, password should have 8 to   10 characters.                        
